{"tid":1574824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民晚上在沙田廣源邨築人鏈　有人向人鏈發射波子","createTime":"2019-09-16T15:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:24:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8325d7b7f6b6b2cc838debeda13dab50e77f5f","tid":1574824,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1480927_2_L_20190916224705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1480927_2_L_20190916224705.jpg&h=b46b7feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民發起晚上在沙田廣源邨築起人鏈，要求政府回應反修例的民間五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n市民在廣源邨巴士總站集合，人鏈一直伸延至恒生大學，陸續有人加入隊伍。不少是區內居民，亦有長者參加，他們手拖著手，不斷高叫口號及唱歌，有人帶同樂器在場伴奏。當橫跨車路時，每當轉行人綠燈，市民便會走出馬路手拖手；當轉紅燈時，市民便會走回行人路及安全島。<br />\n<br />\n南韓藝人金義聖亦有到場參加活動，不少市民上前和他握手及合照，亦有市民揮動南韓國旗及高舉寫上韓文的感謝字句。<br />\n<br />\n活動期間，懷疑有人從遠處向人鏈發射波子，擊中附近一輛私家車的車尾玻璃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480927-20190916.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480927-20190916.htm&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=0a517401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480927-20190916.htm&h=d8702143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480927-20190916.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a867e0123196c70aedae7333f4706490c7a0a08a","tid":1574824,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"722cbf12b95d046a3d5e2d37796f0269a149742c","tid":1574824,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\